snippet.title: Slime Rancher: Plortable Edition Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Slime Rancher: Plortable Edition is available NOW for the Nintendo Switch!

Take the Far, Far Range with you anywhere and play all the content updates in the most slimetastic way to experience Slime Rancher, yet.
